data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home with a generous 2,330 square feet of living space. The open floorplan creates a warm and inviting atmosphere, perfect for both entertaining and everyday living. The spacious bedrooms offer comfort and flexibility, while the back patio provides a lovely outdoor retreat. Enjoy the convenience of a partially fenced yard and a back deck, ideal for gatherings or relaxation. The home features a dedicated laundry room for added convenience. The primary en-suite adds a touch of luxury to your daily routine. Located just 30 minutes from downtown Jacksonville, this property offers the perfect blend of suburban tranquility and easy access to city amenities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new home!
